        description: "successful installations",
      },
      {
        stat: "85%",
        description: "client growth year-over-year",
      },
    ]}
  />-->
<!-- </MainLayout>  -->


<section id="testimonials">
<!--Testimonials section-->
<TestimonialsSectionAlt
title ="Testimonials From Our Customers"
testimonials={[
{
  content: " \"I recently started using the dive management system from Divers Desk, and I must say it has completely transformed the way I handle my dive shop operations. The system is not only user-friendly but also incredibly efficient, allowing me to easily schedule dives, track payments, and effectively oversee and coordinate activities.\n What truly sets this system apart is the exceptional support provided by the team. Whenever I had a question or needed assistance, they were quick to respond and always went above and beyond to ensure that I had everything I needed to succeed. Their dedication to customer service is truly commendable. I can confidently say that Divers Desk, coupled with the outstanding support, has significantly improved my dive shop operations and overall experience. I highly recommend it to anyone in the diving industry looking for a reliable and supportive solution.\" ",
  author: "TI",
  role: "Owner | Jom Adventure",
  avatarSrc: "/images/jomadventure_avatar.avif",
  avatarAlt: "Image Description",
},
// Second testimonial data
{
content:
  " \"We at the Bali Dive Resort and Spa were looking for a paperless registration solution for a long time before we found ‘DiversDesk’.\n'DiversDesk' Scuba Diver Planner is an outstanding tool for any dive operation. Its user-friendly interface makes it easy to navigate, while features like paperless registration and pre-booked dive management streamline operations. Divers can complete all necessary paperwork, including medical forms and liability releases, before arriving, saving time and reducing paper use. \nWe are particularly impressed with the platform’s ease of use and the responsive support team, who listen to and act on our feedback. Regular updates ensure we always have the latest features. We highly recommend ‘DiversDesk’ to dive centers and resorts looking to save time, reduce paper usage, and enhance efficiency.\" ",
author: "Miikka",
role: "Manager | Bali Dive Resort and Spa",
avatarSrc: "/images/bdrs_avatar.avif",
avatarAlt: "Image Description",
},
// Third testimonial data
{
content: " \"I cherish the day we started using the platform 'Diversdesk'. Since then, our booking system has improved in so many ways. We used to send our guests a Word registration form. Now, we send them a link from 'Diversdesk', and the rest practically goes by itself. Creating the booking link is now done under 2 minutes, and the response from our guests is super positive. We don't use any paperwork anymore because the medical form and liability release are filled in online. Super convenient, time saving, and most important, good for the environment!\n Last but not least, payments are much easier now. 'Diversdesk' manages our credit card payments and ensures we receive everything correctly. The service from 'Diversdesk' is exceptional. As someone who struggles with computers, I've asked for help many times, and they've always found a solution. If I can work with this platform, anyone can! Thank you 'Diversdesk' for saving the world 🌎 🫶\" ",
author: "Lars",
role: "Owner | S.E.A. Diving Bali",
avatarSrc: "/images/seadb_avatar.avif",
avatarAlt: "Image Description",
},
// Fourth testimonial data
{
content: " \"Outstanding Software for Diving Center Management. \nAs the manager of a busy diving center, I can't express enough how transformative this software has been for our operations. The user-friendly interface makes it incredibly easy to navigate, even for those who aren't tech-savvy. Setting up schedules, managing bookings, and tracking equipment has never been simpler. \nOne of the standout features is the exceptional customer support. Any time we've had a question or encountered an issue, the support team has been prompt, knowledgeable, and incredibly helpful. They truly go above and beyond to ensure that everything runs smoothly. \nOverall, this software has streamlined our processes, saved us time, and allowed us to focus more on delivering exceptional experiences for our divers. If you're in the diving business and looking for a comprehensive, reliable, and easy-to-use management tool, I highly recommend this software!\" ",
author: "Yves",
role: "Owner | Mantastic Scuba Paradise",
avatarSrc: "/images/mantastic_scuba_avatar.avif",
avatarAlt: "Image Description",
},
// Fifth testimonial data
{
content: " \"We started implementing DiversDesk in October 2024 and the transition from our previous platform to DiversDesk was extremely smooth thanks to the intuitiveness of the tool. DiversDesk development team has always been available and also extremely helpful to guide us through every steps and to keep us in touch of all the new features. Each time we had issues or questions, we had an answer within 24 hours and nothing was left unanswered. DiversDesk team has always been listening to our feedback and requests to suit our company's needs. \n Our guests are also extremely happy and the platform has facilitated our workflow and improved the reliability of our check-in process. \n Many thanks DiversDesk ! 🙏🙏🙏\" ",
author: "Louis",
role: "Manager | Reeflex Divers",
avatarSrc: "/images/louis_avatar.avif",
avatarAlt: "Image Description",
}
]}
/>
</section>

</MainLayout>